\c 2
\s Esiteri anoitwa vahosi panzvimbo yaVhashiti
\p
\v 1 Shure kwezvinhu izvi, pakumira kwekutsamwa kwamambo Ahasuwerusi, wakarangarira Vhashiti nezvaakaita, nechirevo chaakatemerwa.
\v 2 Zvino varanda vamambo vaimushandira vakati: Ngakutsvakirwe mambo vasikana, mhandara dzakanaka pakuonekwa.
\v 3 Zvino mambo ngaagadze vatariri pamatunhu ese eumambo hwake, kuti vaunganidze pamwe vasikana, mhandara dzakanaka pakuonekwa paShushani muzinda, paimba yevakadzi, muruoko rwaHegai mutenwa wamambo, muchengetedzi wevanhukadzi, nekupa zvekuzvinatsa zvavo.
\v 4 Zvino musikana wakanaka pameso amambo ngaave vahosi vamambo panzvimbo yaVhashiti. Chinhi ichi ndokuva chakanaka pameso amambo, iye ndokuita saizvozvo.
\p
\v 5 Kwaiva nemurume muJudha paShushani muzinda, uye zita rake raiva Modhekai, mwanakomana waJairi, mwanakomana waShimei, mwanakomana waKishi, muBhenjamini,
\v 6 waiva atapwa kubva Jerusarema pamwe nevatapwa vaiva vatapwa naJekoniya mambo waJudha, Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi waaiva atapa.
\v 7 Zvino wakarera Hadhasha, ndiye Esiteri, mukunda wababamunini wake; nokuti waiva asina baba kana mai; zvino musikana waiva akanaka pachimiro uye akanaka pakuonekwa, uyo Modhekai baba vake namai vake pavaiva vafa waakatora kuva mukunda wake.
\p
\v 8 Zvino zvakaitika pakwakakanzwikwa murairo wamambo nechirevo chake, uye vasikana vakawanda vaungana pamwe paShushani muzinda muruoko rwaHegai, kuti Esiteri wakatorwa kuiswa mumba mamambo muruoko rwaHegai muchengetedzi wevakadzi.
\v 9 Zvino musikana waiva akanaka pameso ake, iye ndokuwana nyasha kubva kwaari ndokumupa zvekunatsa nemigove yake, nevasikana vakasarudzwa vanomwe kumupa vaibva mumba mamambo; akamubvisa ndokuisa iye nevasikana vake pakanaka peimba yevanhukadzi.
\v 10 Esiteri waiva waiva asina kutaura vanhu vekwake kana rudzi rwake, nokuti Modhekai waiva amuraira kuti asataura.
\v 11 Zvino Modhekai waifamba-famba zuva nezuva pamberi pechivanze cheimba yevanhukadzi, kuziva upenyu hwaEsiteri, uye kuti chii chichaitika kwaari.
\p
\v 12 Zvino pakusvika kwedzoro remusikana umwe neumwe kupinda kuna mambo Ahasuwerusi, pakupedzisira zvaitwa kwaari zvichienderana nemurairo wevanhukadzi, mwedzi mwedzi gumi nemiviri (nokuti saizvozvo kwaizadzisika mazuva ezvekunatsa zvavo, mwedzi mitanhatu nemafuta emura*, mwedzi mitanhatu nezvinonhuhwira zvinotapira, uye ne\add zvimwe\add* zvekunatsa zvevanhukadzi).
\v 13 Zvino neizvozvi musikana wapinda kuna mambo; chingava chii chaaireva achachipiwa kuti aende nacho achibva paimba yevanhukadzi achienda kuimba yamambo.
\v 14 Musikana waipinda, uye mangwanani waidzokera muimba yechipiri yevanhukadzi, kunochengetedzwa naShaashigazi, mutenwa wamambo muchengetedzi wevarongo; waiva asingachapindizve kuna mambo, kunze kwekuti mambo afadzwa naye, ndokudanwa nezita.
\p
\v 15 Zvino dzoro raEsiteri mukunda waAbhihairi babamunini vaModhekai waiva amutora kuva mukunda wake parakasvika kuti apinde kuna mambo, haana kukumbira chinhu kunze kweizvo Hegai mutenwa wamambo, muchengetedzi wevanhukadzi zvaakareva. Zvino Esiteri wakawana nyasha pameso evese vaimuona.
\v 16 Naizvozvo Esiteri wakaiswa kuna mambo Ahasuwerusi muimba yake yeushe mumwedzi wegumi unova mwedzi weTebheti, mugore rechinomwe rekutonga kwake.
\v 17 Mambo ndokuda Esiteri kupfuura vakadzi vese, ndokugamuchira nyasha netsitsi pamberi pake kupfuura mhandara dzese, zvokuti wakaisa korona yake yeumambo mumusoro wake, ndokumuita vahosi vamambo pachinzvimbo chaVhashiti.
\v 18 Zvino mambo wakaita mabiko makuru kumachinda ake ese nevaranda vake vese, mabiko aEsiteri; Akaitirawo matunhu zororo, ndokupa zvipo zvicienderana nesimba ramambo.
\v 19 Zvino pakuunganidzwa kwemhandara rwechipiri, Modhekai akange agere pasuwo ramambo.
\v 20 Esiteri akange achigere kuvazivisa hama dzake kana rudzi rwake, sezvaakarairwa naModhekai; nokuti Esiteri akateerera murairo waModhekai, sezvaaisiita acharerwa naye.
\p
\v 21 Zvino pamazuva iwayo Modhikai agere pasuwo ramambo, varanda vaviri vamambo, Bhigitani naTereshi, pakati pavarindi vomukova, vakatsamwa vakatsvaka kuuraya mambo Ahasuwerusi.
\v 22 Chinhu icho chikazikanwa naModhekai, iye ndokuzivisa vahosi Esiteri, Esiteri akanoudza mambo nezita raModhekai.
\v 23 Zvino vakati vachinzvera chinhu icho, vakawana kuti zvirokwazvo, vese vari vaviri vakasungirirwa pamuti; zvikanyorwa mubhuku yaMakoronike pamberi pamambo.